              "kn": "ತೀರ್ಥಂಕರ ಮತ್ತು ದೇವಿ ಅಭಿಷೇಕ",
              "en": "Tirthankara and Devi Abhishek"
            },
            "printSize": "inline"
          }
        ],
        "tags": [
          "Acharya Shanti Sagar",
          "Padmavati Devi",
          "Abhisheka",
          "Peetha"
        ],
