        "id": "b_021_3",
        "type": "list",
        "content": {
          "kn": [
            "೧. ಣವಣ / Navana = Abhishekas",
            "೨. ಉಪ ಲೇಪನ / Upa Lepana",
            "೩. Pushpa Vrusti:",
            "೪. ಸಮ್ಮಜಣ : Old dravya is cleaned/removed (with water).",
            "೫. ಚುಹಾವಣ : Similar to Upa lepana but only for feet.",
            "೬. ⁠ಪುಲ್ಲಾರೋಹಣ: ಪುಷ್ಪಾರೋಹಣ - Aarohana/ putting flowers garland on pratima. (Not just feet, but entire pratima):"
          ],
          "en": [
            "1. ಣವಣ / Navana = Abhishekas",
            "2. ಉಪ ಲೇಪನ / Upa Lepana: Examples: Gandha upa lepana, Chandana upa lepana",
            "3. Pushpa Vrusti:",
            "4. ಸಮ್ಮಜಣ : Old dravya is cleaned/removed (with water).",
            "5. ಚುಹಾವಣ : Similar to Upa lepana but only for feet.",
            "6. ⁠ಪುಲ್ಲಾರೋಹಣ: ಪುಷ್ಪಾರೋಹಣ - Aarohana/ putting flowers garland on pratima. (Not just feet, but entire pratima):"
          ]
        },
